snippet.title: New Cycle - Official Trailer
snippet.description: New Cycle is a base-builder simulation game where a solar flare devastates the world. 50 years later, you're tasked with helping humanity survive by rebuilding a metropolis city. Manage their morale, efficiency, workforce size, develop forgotten technologies, and enact societal rules to bring upon a new world. New Cycle is coming to PC Early Access this year.
